      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALISON'S MISSION (1) collided in the run and missed the frame when fifth (17.90) at this track over 297m in a Novice race. Little luck latest and can bounce back to best. MAKUTZ (8) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Finished in the minors last time when third (17.73) at this track making it back to back placings. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Must be included in calculations. WEST ON RICKY (2) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 17.83 beating That's So Ted. Can make it two on the bounce. SHINBONER AXEL (3) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
